---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="개발 / 서버 / 일본 생활 같은 거 그냥 쓰는 블로그."
    />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="home">
      <section class="hero">
        <h1>sAz의 항해기록</h1>
        <p>개발 / 서버 / 일본 생활 같은 거 그냥 쓰는 블로그.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="home-note">
        <p>
          아직 정리 중인 블로그입니다. 셋업/구조 정리하면서 천천히 글을 쌓을
          예정.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .home {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero p {
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .home-note {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    opacity: 0.8;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
</style>